title: Walker's Paradise, Vintage Building & Laundry On-Site - 2 Weeks Free
posting_body: ['Large Studio 2 Blocks from King Street Station - 2 Weeks Free Rent!', 'Property Address', '311 6TH AVE S UNIT 217 | SEATTLE, WA 98104', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Governor Apartments - Seattle Property Management Associates', 'Description', 'The Governor is located in the heart of the International District offering a walk score of 98!', 'This is ideal for easy access to Metro/Sound Transit/Light Rail, and all that Downtown Seattle has to offer.', 'This is a beautiful studio, with hard to find amenities in a Seattle studio apartment.', 'The Governor Building is a well maintained historic building, with amazing architectural details.', 'Located just one block from the International District Station, serving Link Light Rail, Sound Transit, King County Metro, Seattle Streetcar.', 'Just 2 blocks from King Street Station, serving Amtrak, and Sounder Commuter trains.', 'With-in walking distance of Lumen Field/Event Center, and T-Mobile Park.', 'At the time of application, we require payment of the $25 application fee per person and a $1000 deposit that is then applied to the refundable security deposit upon approval.', 'This building is no smoking and no dogs- cats are allowed.', 'There is a $50 utility fee for water, sewer, and garbage.', 'For more information or to schedule a showing, please contact Josh', 'show contact info', 'Feel free to view all of our property vacancies at:', '<URL>', 'Amenities', 'Vintage Building', 'On-Site Management', 'Controlled Access', 'Laundry On Site', 'Secure Entry', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 395', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,195.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
